content:
Sorry for my english.
If the pixel 4A is charging, gmail notifications arrive instantly; if it is not charging and the screen is on, notifications arrive instantly. If it is not charging and the screen is off (standby), notifications will not arrive, or arrive very late.
My settings:
adaptive battery OFF;
battery optimization (for gmail) OFF;
notifications for every new message ENABLED;
background data ENABLED;
clear the cache of gmail app;
OS updated;
gmail app updated;
